<idea-plugin>
    <id>com.mengzz.FluentFormatter</id>
    <name>Fluent Formatter</name>
    <vendor email="863561164@qq.com" url="https://github.com/Mengzuozhu/FluentFormatter">zuozhu.meng</vendor>

    <description><![CDATA[

    <p><a href="https://github.com/Mengzuozhu/FluentFormatter">GitHub</a></p>
    <p>Format the code in a fluent style.</p>
    <p>Step：</p>
    <p>1. Select the code</p>
    <p>2. Use shortcut keys <b>Alt+Enter</b></p>
    <p>3. Select <b>Fluent format</b></p>

    <p>格式化代码为流式风格</p>
    <p>使用步骤：</p>
    <p>1. 选中需格式化的代码</p>
    <p>2. 使用快捷键<b>Alt+Enter</b></p>
    <p>3. 选择<b>Fluent format</b></p>
    ]]></description>

    <depends>com.intellij.modules.platform</depends>

    <extensions defaultExtensionNs="com.intellij">
        <intentionAction>
            <className>com.mengzz.fluentformatter.FluentFormatterAction</className>
        </intentionAction>
    </extensions>

    <actions>
    </actions>
</idea-plugin>
